description = "A grizzled veteran with a scarred face and one milky eye. Captain Harken was once the commander of Larton's garrison - now he leads the last five guards who remained when the rest fled or died. His armor is dented and patched, his sword notched from too many battles. He stands at the barricades day and night, refusing to abandon the survivors he has sworn to protect. He speaks little, but his grim determination gives the others hope."
